title: NDC Sydney 2024
presenter: Matt Goldman, William Liebenberg, Jernej Kavka, Luke Parker, Adam Cogan and more
eventShortDescription:
NDC Sydney 2024 will be an in-person event, held 12-16 February 2024 at the Hilton Sydney. It's a five-day event comprised of 2-days deep-dive workshops, followed by 3 conference days with multiple simultaneous tracks.

SSW'ers presenting:

  • Matt Goldman

  • William Liebenberg

  • Luke Parker

  • Jernej Kavka

  • Adam Cogan

Meet us there! 🙂

Note: SSW does not host this event.
